review_blob: Bottle, dark brown smells of licorice extremly overpowering i couldnt stand to take another taste..needless to say this is a definate drain pour im almost scared to try the others that came in this gift set despite what others are saying..

Nitro Can, poured with a very beautiful long lasting creamy head as you would expect froma a nitorcan color was nicea and black..as for taste slight choclate coffee almost almondy. but very thin and watery. over all some what decent .

Bottle nice white head diminished quickly.
taste was of pine and orange ,nice hoppy flavor very smooth indede. A pleasent reward after a hard days work
